title: updated TensorFlow official example: cifar10
body_html:
I found a problem in the official example: cifar10

It not working in the newest TensorFlow because of API change.

But it's an excellent tutorials for newcomer.

So i updated it and hope more people could see it.

Except API changes,I didn't do any other change.

I hope this tutorials can add to official example again.
